---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="4. Execution Plan">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16">
            <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-pistos-black mb-6 leading-tight">
                The Roadmap: <span class="text-pistos-red">Two Layers Only.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted max-w-2xl">
                Building a monolithic system from day one creates immense friction. Instead, we deploy in two strategic, highly-focused layers.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
            
            <!-- Layer 1 -->
            <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded border border-pistos-black bg-pistos-surface shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden group" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity transform group-hover:scale-110">
                    <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-48 h-48 text-pistos-black"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-pistos-black text-white font-mono font-bold text-lg rounded-sm">L1</div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-pistos-black">Digital Handshake</h2>
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Astro / Public Facing</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl text-lg">
                        A fast, credible public website that acts as a second handshake after personal contact. Its job is to say: "If you are looking for serious, long-term value, you are in the right place."
                    </p>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-pistos-border pt-6 mt-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-pistos-black mb-3">Key Characteristics</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-pistos-black">
                                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-red shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Performance-first (SEO, Core Web Vitals)</span></li>
                                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-red shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>No accounts, no dashboards, no complexity</span></li>
                                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-red shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Minimal lead capture (Credibility is the product)</span></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Layer 2 -->
            <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded border border-pistos-border bg-[#FAFAFA] relative overflow-hidden group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity transform group-hover:scale-110">
                    <i data-lucide="server" class="w-48 h-48 text-pistos-black"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-white border border-pistos-border text-pistos-black font-mono font-bold text-lg rounded-sm">L2</div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-pistos-black">Decision Support Web App</h2>
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Next.js / Private Access</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl text-lg">
                        A private, interactive application that helps potential clients make informed decisions and gives the company insight into what clients care about. Access requires phone number authentication.
                    </p>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-pistos-border pt-6 mt-6">
                        <!-- Tools Grid -->
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-pistos-black mb-1">Client-Facing Tools</h4>
                            <div class="bg-white border border-pistos-border p-3 rounded">
                                <div class="font-medium text-sm text-pistos-black">1. Cost Estimation</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-pistos-muted mt-1">Clear ranges and trade-offs. No fake precision.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white border border-pistos-border p-3 rounded">
                                <div class="font-medium text-sm text-pistos-black">2. Jurisdiction Helper</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-pistos-muted mt-1">Mainland vs Free Zone guidance.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white border border-pistos-border p-3 rounded">
                                <div class="font-medium text-sm text-pistos-black">3. Trade Name Checker</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-pistos-muted mt-1">Early validation / conflict awareness.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white border border-pistos-border p-3 rounded">
                                <div class="font-medium text-sm text-pistos-black">4. Activity Selector</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-pistos-muted mt-1">Helps users narrow down suitable activities.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white border border-pistos-border p-3 border-l-4 border-l-pistos-red rounded">
                                <div class="font-medium text-sm text-pistos-black">5. Gov't API Integration</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-pistos-muted mt-1">Live linking to DED (e.g. instant Trade Name Checker).</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Internal Vis & Addon -->
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-pistos-black mb-3">Internal Visibility</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-pistos-black">
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><i data-lucide="eye" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-muted shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Staff can see tool usage & generated outputs</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><i data-lucide="filter" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-muted shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Used for precise follow-up, NOT a full CRM</span></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="bg-pistos-surface border border-pistos-red/30 p-4 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-pistos-red to-transparent"></div>
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="bot" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-red"></i>
                                    <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-pistos-black">Optional Add-On: AI Assistant</span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-xs text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed">Retrieval-based (approved resources only). Strictly internal to Layer 2. Requires explicit API budget approval.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Future Expansions -->
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-pistos-border" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 mb-4">
                    <i data-lucide="fast-forward" class="w-6 h-6 text-pistos-red mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-pistos-black">Future Expansions (What can be added later)</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted">Once Layers 1 and 2 are stable, the architecture easily supports infinite scaling. Examples of future additions:</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pl-10">
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded">
                        <strong class="text-xs text-pistos-black block mb-1">Government API Integration</strong>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Live linking to DED/Free Zone portals for instant name reservation and license status.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded">
                        <strong class="text-xs text-pistos-black block mb-1">Digital Vault & E-Signatures</strong>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Secure document uploads with integrated OCR and legally binding digital contract signing.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded">
                        <strong class="text-xs text-pistos-black block mb-1">Automated PRO Workflows</strong>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Ticketing systems for visa processing, emirates ID tracking, and medical scheduling.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded">
                        <strong class="text-xs text-pistos-black block mb-1">Corporate Tax Ecosystem</strong>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Direct upsells and dashboards for 'The One Accountant' featuring live bookkeeping metrics.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Delivery Sequence -->
            <div class="mt-12 bg-pistos-black text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-6 flex items-center"><i data-lucide="rocket" class="w-5 h-5 mr-3 text-pistos-red"></i>Delivery Sequence</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:space-x-4 space-y-4 md:space-y-0 text-sm font-medium">
                    <div class="flex-1 border border-white/20 p-4 rounded flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span>1. Ship Layer 1</span>
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-pistos-red"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center opacity-50 hidden md:flex">
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 border border-white/20 p-4 rounded opacity-70">
                        2. Ship Layer 2
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center opacity-50 hidden md:flex">
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 border border-white/20 p-4 rounded opacity-50 border-dashed">
                        3. AI Add-on (Optional)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-start mt-24 mb-32">
            <a href="/motion" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black font-medium transition-colors">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                <span>Prev: 5. Motion Rationale</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
